<img src="Enrolled_An_Act.JPG" alt="">
</div>
<ul><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexHang">To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to repeal the excise tax on high cost employer-sponsored health coverage.</p></ul>
<p></p>
<p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndent"><em> Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the
		United States of America in Congress assembled, </em><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexHang"><a href="#H5BC2CD415BB34FA29798052E64A29ABA" id="toc-H5BC2CD415BB34FA29798052E64A29ABA"><div class="lbexHangWithMargin" style="clear:both;">
