</div></a></p><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndent"><p style="text-align:left">This Act may be cited as the Coronavirus Aid, Relief, and Economic Security Act or the CARES Act.</p></p><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexHang"><a href="#H5E3E6A75BA154F8694D97A1161AC4E53" id="toc-H5E3E6A75BA154F8694D97A1161AC4E53"><div class="lbexHangWithMargin" style="clear:both;">
