<a href="#toc-H263F4EADFD224F3B923348BA9069DD0D" id="H263F4EADFD224F3B923348BA9069DD0D">TITLE VIMISCELLANEOUS PROVISIONS<p></p></a>
</div></span><span><span class="lbexTocSectionOLC"><br><a href="#toc-H01E28A58DD1E4BD0856501D34883AC7E" id="H01E28A58DD1E4BD0856501D34883AC7E">Sec. 6001. COVID19 borrowing authority for the United States Postal Service.</a></span></span><span><span class="lbexTocSectionOLC"><br><a href="#toc-HC20C189870CA4A60A9D7CA9CC3BD41E4" id="HC20C189870CA4A60A9D7CA9CC3BD41E4">Sec. 6002. Emergency designation.</a></span></span><span><div style="text-align:center" class="lbexTocDivisionOLC">
