mount and inserting (A) Credit is refundable.If the amount; and</p></p><a id="HC87CDD225CC04C37B0F48B12684CC179"> </a><p style="margin-left: -2em;"><p class="lbexIndentSubpar">(B) by adding at the end the following:<p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndentClause"><a id="HBBC0C37E1CB04E94A405EBBDF474A0ED"> </a><p style="margin-left: -2em;"><p class="lbexIndentSubpar">(B) <span style="font-size:110%; text-transform: capitalize ">A</span>DVANCING CREDIT.In anticipation of the credit, including the refundable portion under subparagraph (A), the credit may be advanced, according to forms and instructions provided by the Secretary, up to an amount calculated under subsection (a), subject to the limits under subsection (b), both calculated through the end of the most recent payroll period in the quarter.;</p></p></p></p></p></p></p><a id="HC3D8F91CC23C4211AAB48A1D59D93683"> </a><p style="margin-left: 0em;"><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndentParagraph">(2) in subsection (f)<a id="H4E16084A5C57415C81700AD85548D170"> </a><p style="margin-left: -2em;"><p class="lbexIndentSubpar">(A) in paragraph (4), by striking , and and inserting a comma;</p></p><a id="HDC15948CDA854B31A90680C22D7AC2B2"> </a><p style="margin-left: -2em;"><p class="lbexIndentSubpar">(B) in paragraph (5), by striking the period at the end and inserting , and; and</p></p><a id="HA91927533EB745AEB3867EEE09EA0AB7"> </a><p style="margin-left: -2em;"><p class="lbexIndentSubpar">(C) by adding at the end the following:<p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndentClause"><a id="HDADD7A2F52024C0FA0D0FBE62029AFE4"> </a><p style="margin-left: 0em;"><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndentParagraph">(6) regulations or other guidance to permit the advancement of the credit determined under subsection (a).; and</p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p><a id="H72A89F1ABA8A4FD388BD1CF1FE988B84"> </a><p style="text-align:left" class="lbexIndent">(c) by inserting after subsection (h) the following new subsection:<p style="